Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Onions
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.87,0:01:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready, Gary?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:45.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(756,830)}洋葱
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再加一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just one more thing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peanuts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我们的花生罐空了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, our peanuts jar is totally empty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.95,0:02:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道还有一个能找到花生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know one other place we can find peanuts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我窗台还种了这株花生盆栽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I still have these
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,peanut plants growing in the windowsill
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,口感不太一样没啥大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little texture never hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There we go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.15,0:02:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣代一定会非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This sundae's going to taste great
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不来一起吃吗  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to help me, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.20,0:02:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.80,0:02:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能多吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More for me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俗话说得好  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what they say, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.15,0:02:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我轻松得宛如星期天的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm easy like Sunday morning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:46.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(748,476)}清晨
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  来看看我的待办事项单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, let's see my to do list
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go to work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样可不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得要适合星期天做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need the one for Sunday
