Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm confused
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.70,0:04:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  大家都在躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, everyone is running away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, building
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't either
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是你穿着不得体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the way you're dressed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是你声音难听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's your voice
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.30,0:04:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就可能是因为你很丑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it's just because you're ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ugly?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定是在开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好做个照镜测试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better try the reflection test
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不可能会丑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't be ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't be
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能丑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't be ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我丑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I ugly?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我丑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I ugly?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很丑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.95,0:05:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我能不能借点浴珠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, can I borrow some bath beads?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像其他人那样躲着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run away like all the others
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.47,0:06:22.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人想要像我这样丑的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:22.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one would want a friend as ugly as I am
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些人当然想了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure they would
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的丑陋会让他们对自己长相更自信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It makes them feel better about the way they look
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲个故事应该可以让你振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe a story will cheer you up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.65,0:06:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个故事叫  丑陋的藤壶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's called "The Ugly Barnacle"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前  有一只丑陋的藤壶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once, there was an ugly barnacle
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他把大家都丑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was so ugly that everyone died
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The end
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That didn't help at all
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.85,0:06:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经丑多久了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long have I been ugly, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自打我记事起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as I can remember
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.70,0:06:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这个可怜的丑东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You poor ugly thing, you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我羞愧难当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so ashamed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.72,0:07:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生活跌入谷底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm spiralling
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不跌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spiralling over
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,学我应对问题的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just do what I do when I have problems
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喊出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scream
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.67,0:07:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟快来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll help you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK now, say it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你要想心里舒服点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you're never going to feel better
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就别把东西堵胸口上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until you get this thing off your chest
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.95,0:07:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.90,0:07:39.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很丑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:39.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你很丑  而且还什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ugly and what?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Square?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.66,0:07:44.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Proud
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很丑  而且很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ugly, and I'm proud
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.37,0:07:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.92,0:07:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it louder
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很丑  而且很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ugly, and I'm proud
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再大声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Louder
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很丑  而且很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ugly, and I'm proud
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再大声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Louder
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很丑  而且很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ugly, and I'm proud
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很丑  而且很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am ugly, and I'm proud
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很丑  而且很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ugly, and I'm proud
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what he calls it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That felt great
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全身充满力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel empowered
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你现在想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what do you want to do now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.17,0:08:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看电影怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,392)}礁石影院
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丑陋海绵借过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ugly sponge coming through
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家尊重自尊自爱的美德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People respect self-esteem
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我很丑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm very ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你一样也要安心看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you should enjoy the movie anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我的丑陋不会打扰到你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope my horrible ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,won't be a distraction to you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not at all, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管他的事了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just a--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do this, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我试了又试  可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've tried, and I've tried, but--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.42,0:09:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的自信还只是停留在表面工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not always as confident as I look
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是回去躲起来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I better just go back and hide
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you people?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害怕看他的丑脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Afraid to look ugliness in the face?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很丑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's ugly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.12,0:09:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.15,0:09:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.99,0:09:23.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:23.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.08,0:09:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们大家都给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want all of you to look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们全跑了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They all ran away, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,零食吧那边肯定没人排队了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet there's no line at the snack bar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(898,438)}零食
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,员工肯定是去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They must be on break
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚记起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just remembered
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带了点花生洋葱圣代  可以分着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got some of my peanut onion sundae we can share
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.62,0:09:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着就好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks great
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去趟厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta go to the restroom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.07,0:10:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肥皂用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm out of soap
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.12,0:10:04.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:04.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是要点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want some
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.12,0:10:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钱拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's my money
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你收下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收下  然后马上走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it, and go away
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手没那么脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hands aren't that dirty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想不想听个厕所笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you guys want to hear a bathroom joke?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是想杀了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You trying to kill us?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被传染丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  里面没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, is everything OK in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在里面干什么  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in there, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to know?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你头上为什么套了个袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why is that bag on your head?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No reason
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了你把丑传染给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except you gave me the ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不能这样子出去见人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't go out looking like this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.55,0:10:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想我们刚刚还说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just remember what we talked about
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自豪力量大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's power in pride
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对你来说可能没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That may be fine for you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我原先长相特漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I was one of the beautiful people
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.71,0:11:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在看看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我几乎都跟你一样丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm almost as ugly as you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.61,0:11:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在想  要是我跟那位一样丑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always thought, if I was as ugly as that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不知道要怎么办才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I would do
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈会怎么说我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's my mom going to say?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  要是我姐姐发现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh, if my sister finds out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.20,0:11:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我没有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I don't have a sister
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是银行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If the bank--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然鞋子差或者头发差是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean it's one thing if you have bad shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or even bad hair
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.93,0:11:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.67,0:11:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不丑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.88,0:11:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你口气臭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your breath stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really bad
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a relief
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.60,0:11:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吃什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what did you eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点烤牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some roast beef
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.02,0:11:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点鸡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some chicken
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.85,0:11:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.05,0:11:37.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:37.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你早上吃的啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点烤牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some roast beef
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.06,0:11:40.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点鸡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:40.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some chicken
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.94,0:11:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.97,0:11:42.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:42.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吃了点你的圣代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I had some of your sundae
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.15,0:11:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sundae
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.82,0:11:52.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  是我圣代让我们口气特别臭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:52.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, my sundae gave us rancid breath
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.70,0:11:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是  我们不丑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're not ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just stink
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stink?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.07,0:12:15.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:15.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We stink
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,220)}假发
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We stink
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.36,0:12:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.12,0:12:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I stink
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.79,0:12:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶臭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reek
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闻我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smell me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.10,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(355,355)\fsp50\fs160\c&H00FFA9&}珍珍爱管事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(446,410)\frz20.1}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:38.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,518)\frz17.45}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(436,322)\frz19.88}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.84\pos(318,354)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.84\pos(466,642)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(268,556)\frz19.67}插曲演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(544,340)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体蟹堡王员工  请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All Krusty Krew employees, attention
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作都给我快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get the anchors out of your pants
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到我办公室报到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and report to me office
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.84,0:12:52.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:52.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That will be all
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要宣布一件重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have an important announcement to make
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新锅铲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The new spatulas are here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.16,0:13:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐下  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sit down, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有新锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no new spatulas
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How disappointing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都知道我女儿珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You men know me daughter, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她长得特别快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's growing up fast
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.11,0:13:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像我昨天才教她跃出水面一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It seems like it was just yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was teaching her how to breach
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的哺乳类小天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me mammalian angel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyway, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.48,0:13:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她暑假期间要来蟹堡王打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so she's going to be working here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,during her summer vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她有不少新鲜点子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's got a lot of fresh ideas
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以引来饿肚子的新客
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to bring in some hungry customers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.37,0:13:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There she blows
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  知不知道这表示什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, do you realize what this means?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有新锅铲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No new spatulas
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.19,0:13:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会有没礼貌青少年要来教我们做事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some bratty teenager's coming in here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to tell us what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种事绝对不能有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't have that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们年纪比她大  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have seniority, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们要齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we'll work together to
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保护我们可悲的职位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,protect our pathetic positions
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okie dokie, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后新锅铲就能到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then we'll get those new spatulas
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, men
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我的珍珍打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say hello to me Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  柱柱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Pole
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我十分高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It makes me jolly as a roger
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你终于来参与家族产业了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to finally have you aboard the family business
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我有不少新点子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I have so many new ideas
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经能闻到钱的味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can smell the money already
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要找我的话就来办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be in my office if you need me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.00,0:14:12.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盒子里有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:12.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in the box?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like surprises
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.79,0:14:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then close your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目前还算喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I like it so far
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是新款蟹堡王员工服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the new Krusty Krew uniform
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I designed it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机会来了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跟她说你对新员工服的真正感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now tell her how you really feel about that uniform
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.27,0:14:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  这是史上最棒的制服了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, this is the greatest uniform ever
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fish paste
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你样子好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob, you look so adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.35,0:14:45.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都能把你吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:45.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could just eat you up
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本品不在菜单上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this item's not on the menu
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽说这不太可能  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't think it was possible, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你样子比平常还要可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you look even more ridiculous than usual
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别嫉妒人家  章鱼叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be jealous, Uncle Squiddy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也给你做了一套哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made one for you, too
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.55,0:15:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't bother
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有傻子才会去穿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only a fool would wear that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停航  船员们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Avast, ye shipmates
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新员工服是不是让你们很震撼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't these just shiver your timbers?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶快穿上  水手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get that suit on, sailor
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是花了钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's already been paid for
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暴怒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rage
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,气愤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fury
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恼火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Irritation
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Humiliation
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥真是个缺心眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is such a barnacle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老古板一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A stick in the sand
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你不一样  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可有型了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are full of style
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.96,0:15:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Totally, SB
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你洋溢着时尚气息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ooze fashion
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.45,0:15:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我对这老地方有些特炫的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I've got some completely coral concepts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for this old joint
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要有你这样的天赋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to need someone with your kind of talent
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.65,0:15:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来给我帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在帮蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I have been trying to get Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给这地方改一改
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make some changes around here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.63,0:15:49.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了我的女生天性还有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:49.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, with my girlish instincts and your, um
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sponginess
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就能把这个破烂餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll turn this worn out lunch waggon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.77,0:15:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变成青少年天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into a teenage paradise
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你更喜欢哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what do you like better--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.50,0:16:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,萌堡王还是怪堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Kutie Krab or the Kooky Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,容我问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dare I ask
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换了新面貌就要取个新名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The new name for our new look
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王这个旧名字还是弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, the Krusty Krab has got to go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名字一听就屑  谁还会来这吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to eat at a place they think is crusty?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  名字起得很烂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, sure, it's a terrible name
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这地方也很烂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but this is a terrible place
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此名字的事就别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the name should be left alone
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱堡王怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about the Khaotic Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲堡王怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about the Kissy Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.15,0:16:29.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:29.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The King Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糖堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Kandy Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Kool Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者牛仔堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or the Kowboy Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卷堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Kurly Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Kreepy Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杀堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Killer Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.42,0:16:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too scary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Kuddly Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(298,618)}抱堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹把蟹堡王卖出去了  真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a shame old man Krab sold the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a darn shame
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小姐  你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, lady, do you know
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这附近哪里可以吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where we can get something to eat around here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了  我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, I quit
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算有青少年专属的酷地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally a cool place for teens
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.49,0:17:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}舒心感觉时刻在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Feeling so good all-around
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以好好在这放开了耍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to just, you know, hang out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.47,0:17:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  你可真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, you're a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.48,0:17:26.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}知道有这座神奇小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:26.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Think you got such a magical town
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些年轻新潮的新客都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All these young, hip new customers
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.86,0:17:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}数天前我游向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}I swam so far the other day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥太土了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phooey on Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.01,0:17:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全跟不上时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can't keep up with the times
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.15,0:17:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}想找到这神奇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}To try to find this magical place
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真有见识  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a true visionary, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,视力正常  见得确实多
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.16,0:17:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}距离一定很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do have 20/20 vision
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}It's gotta be at somewhere far
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新潮客也得吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hip people have to eat, too
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}还有鱼儿在畅游
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Somewhere down where all the fish are
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回烤架那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人也许兴奋热情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The customers may be hot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.44,0:17:45.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}总有一天我可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:45.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Someday, I'll find it if I keep trying
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我烤架可更热
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but my grill is hotter
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, order up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}在路上我会时刻微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Until then, I'll just keep smiling
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两份沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two salads
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}想想我到过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Thinking about the places I've been
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.37,0:17:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never heard of it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.05,0:17:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得潮下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta stay hip
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.48,0:17:56.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}当我在梦中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:56.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}While moving around inside my dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能落得笨蛋老章鱼那种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to end up like silly old Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.67,0:17:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可沙拉到底是个什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what in the name of Davy Jones's locker is a salad?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.31,0:17:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}色彩在波浪下舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Colors dance beneath the waves
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.77,0:18:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}美好一天美好结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Such a beautiful end to a beautiful day
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两份沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two salads
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.86,0:18:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gross
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}舒心感觉时刻在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Feeling so good all-around
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种东西可不是沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those aren't salads
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.95,0:18:06.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:06.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take those back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去掉面包  肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remove the bun, the patty
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.92,0:18:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,110)}知道有这座神奇小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,165)}Think you got such a magical town
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有调料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the condiments
