Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that leaves just lettuce and tomato
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.62,0:18:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没面包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No buns
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.80,0:18:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很新潮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's hip
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No patties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.20,0:18:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happening
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.45,0:18:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  这绝对是我见过最酷的菜品了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that's definitely the coolest meal I ever saw
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is so cool
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.85,0:18:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两份沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two salads
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was awful
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我以后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope I never
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.28,0:18:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不会把好端端的蟹黄堡分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have to tear apart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a perfectly good Krabby Patty ever again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小心脏可受不住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think my heart can take it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.99,0:18:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤架哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the grill?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're a hip guy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油炸食品已经过气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know fried foods are O-U-T, out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我定的新菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check out this new menu I came up with
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沙拉和茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salad and tea
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(560,172)}抱堡王菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可蟹黄堡哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But where are the Krabby patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  那种东西可不潮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silly, those aren't hip
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意再也用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't be needing that thing anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.05,0:19:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之有件更有意思的事情要让你去做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got something more fun for you to do, anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  要搭便车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, you need a ride?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.22,0:19:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去大傻蛋大会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just on my way to the big doofus convention
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is humiliating
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是煎炸厨师  该死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a fry cook, darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以拿走我的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can take away my spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可要是你拿走我的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but when you take away my dignity
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's when I get mad
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要冲进蟹老板的办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to march right into Mr. Krabs's office
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他说这样太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and tell him this is just too much
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(882,620)}快来抱堡王用餐
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我能跟你谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, could I talk to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.50,0:19:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来吧  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in, me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.82,0:19:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a seat
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喜不喜欢我新办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you just love me new office?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍特地给我设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearlie designed it for me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we've got a problem
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你坐的这个40块钱的椅子舒不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the neatest $40 chair you ever sat in?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我有个坏消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I've got some bad news
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的抱抱经理兔怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about my cuddly executive bunny?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.02,0:20:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只需五次支付九块九五即可减压
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reduces stress for only five easy payment of $9.95
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.59,0:20:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  珍珍在毁掉蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, Pearl is ruining the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.87,0:20:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍可是在拯救蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, Pearl is saving the Krustry Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  抱堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, the Kuddly Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.22,0:20:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了这些20块钱的漂亮海独角兽挂饰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would we do without these beautiful $20
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sea unicorn wall hangers?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了这些35块的心型灯我们还怎么活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could we have ever survived
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without these $35 heart lights?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.74,0:20:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,桌子不放海蕨  日子还能怎么过下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could we go on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without a sea fern on every last table?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.82,0:20:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别潮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's hip
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别炫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's coral
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别费钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's losing money
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.85,0:20:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不能就这么开除我的宝贝女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I can't fire me pride and joy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她脆弱的心灵会碎掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It would break her fragile little heart
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啦  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定还有别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's another way
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.08,0:20:52.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来开除她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:52.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could fire her
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她就算恨你也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's OK if she hates you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是这么说的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not what I said, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好  安排妥当了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great then, it's all settled
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你开除珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fire Pearlie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.67,0:20:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我躲办公室里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:20:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll hide in the office
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.22,0:21:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也太粗鲁了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Totally rude, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  你能来厨房一小会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, could I see you in the kitchen for a second?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么向她交代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I going to break it to her?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没开除过谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never fired anyone before
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我就直接开口了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I just got to say it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, you're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, here it goes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做的事全都没效果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing I do is working
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.71,0:21:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然有效了  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, it is, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看那些新潮小伙子吃着沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all the hip, young people eating salads
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打上班第一天起我就想让自己被开除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to get fired since day one
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直在假装喜欢蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was only pretending to like this place
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好取悦老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to please Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.53,0:21:47.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这工作严重打乱了我的社交生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:47.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This job is cutting majorly into my social life
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob, what should I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.50,0:21:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.90,0:21:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以假装开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could pretend to fire you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会我就去挨蟹老板的骂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take the heat from old man Krabs later
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  你真会为我那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, you'd really do that for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a great pal, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么谢谢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can I ever thank you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把我掰成两半了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to break me in half
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.25,0:22:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:13.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168,552)}办公室
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.40,0:22:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.70,0:22:13.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:13.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要装得像一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to make this convincing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.74,0:22:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  我有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, I need to have a word with you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.47,0:22:19.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.56,0:22:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it goes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道我能不能忍心听下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can bear to listen
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.48,0:22:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是因为你工作做得不到位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not that you haven't done a good job around here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.55,0:22:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just that--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.12,0:22:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别对她那么强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be too hard on her now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.82,0:22:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么非得要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be this way?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.96,0:22:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要为大局着想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's for the best
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要为大家都好  就得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we feel it might be in everybody's best interest if--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.59,0:22:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让他这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't let him do this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.95,0:22:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你继续吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get on with it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.05,0:22:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, you're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.02,0:22:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, gang
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.49,0:22:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,商场等着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mall waits
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.20,0:22:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs, I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.97,0:23:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearlie
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.05,0:23:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是二十块吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that a 20?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.50,0:23:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.27,0:23:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么能对我的骨肉做出这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how could we have done such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to me own flesh and blood?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.52,0:23:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.32,0:23:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍心甘情愿接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl took it just fine
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实她好像还挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, she seemed kind of happy
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.83,0:23:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.72,0:23:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她去追求更伟大的事业了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's off to bigger and better things
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.30,0:23:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是我的女儿  坚强无比
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me girl, tough as nails
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.65,0:23:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟她老爸一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like her old man
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.95,0:23:27.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可买了这么多东西  要怎么回本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how am I going to get my money back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for all this stuff?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.45,0:23:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.12,0:23:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.71,0:23:38.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:38.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.60,0:23:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还只花了我一年的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it only cost me one year's salary
